<blockquote>有幾長途，做乜要一齊搭？</blockquote><br />\n3至4個鐘<br />\n無講咩原因，就係話順路一齊搭"},{"pid":"794f0dd2993e2d8139e259ad6b34f88b0f5cb7ac","tid":422943,"uid":63132,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:04:12.000Z","msg":"我明,一男一女出街,<br />\n就算係起公眾地方,<br />\n都會有啲吃醋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但依啲都算係正常社交,<br />\n係順路一齊去,又唔係特登去約會,<br />\n可能係你佔有慾大咗少少,<br />\n除非你陪女朋友一齊去囉,<br />\n如果唔係無理由唔比人地一齊,<br />\n要個女仔自己一個返嘅,<br />\n比多啲信任,放鬆下啦~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d46c8308165dc269c39b107e99b944e116fccb46","tid":422943,"uid":3935,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:04:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有幾長途，做乜要一齊搭？</blockquote><br />\n3至4個鐘<br />\n無講咩原因，就係話順路一齊搭</blockquote><br />\n你女朋友究竟住邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cdc4188539a355c62f896eeb593503656354307","tid":422943,"uid":11447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:04:50.000Z","msg":"男人<br />\n唔補好易老<br />\n唔睇實好易帽"},{"pid":"4fdbf7fd252e30f2e8928b706e3b37ac3e8f67d3","tid":422943,"uid":61697,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:08:51.000Z","msg":"佢自己一個女仔搭車比陌生男人騷擾仲驚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2700eed0d96279031642d000b2135df237eb1ef","tid":422943,"uid":133518,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:11:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我明,一男一女出街,<br />\n就算係起公眾地方,<br />\n都會有啲吃醋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但依啲都算係正常社交,<br />\n係順路一齊去,又唔係特登去約會,<br />\n可能係你佔有慾大咗少少,<br />\n除非你陪女朋友一齊去囉,<br />\n如果唔係無理由唔比人地一齊,<br />\n要個女仔自己一個返嘅,<br />\n比多啲信任,放鬆下啦~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我的確係易呷醋<br />\n而佢算係好外向果類型<br />\n以前都因為類似既問題講過嘈過<br />\n但係佢就岩岩同我講同個男仔約好左<br />\n重買埋飛，先斬後奏<br />\n重問我會唔呷醋<br />\n我呷醋又點呀，約又約左，飛又買好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e46fd6135e72f665eb6535ce5642b789d1a4a0d1","tid":422943,"uid":133518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:11:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有幾長途，做乜要一齊搭？</blockquote><br />\n3至4個鐘<br />\n無講咩原因，就係話順路一齊搭</blockquote><br />\n你女朋友究竟住邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢返大陸"},{"pid":"a3397eb146ac93491ca8e045abe1efe54abdf31f","tid":422943,"uid":67896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:13:17.000Z","msg":"無人同佢一齊搭你仲驚喎<br />\n自己一個女仔<br />\n<br />\n放心啦 長途車咁多人出出入入望住 有咩好驚"},{"pid":"66161bf153fa84b7b9d78582f1abfc1bb8e48720","tid":422943,"uid":133518,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:13:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢自己一個女仔搭車比陌生男人騷擾仲驚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我知，但係個心真係好唔舒服<br />\n不過依家大陸D車周圍都有cam<br />\n比以前安全"},{"pid":"af36afe6a25d080465efd32689ed9e70aad948cb","tid":422943,"uid":133518,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:15:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無人同佢一齊搭你仲驚喎<br />\n自己一個女仔<br />\n<br />\n放心啦 長途車咁多人出出入入望住 有咩好驚</blockquote><br />\n多人出出入入我先唔擔心安全<br />\n一諗到女朋友同個人一齊坐埋啲又逼又窄既位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a28b133295c359d3fbd8af76ad322f318e31b4b6","tid":422943,"uid":915,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:20:38.000Z","msg":"我係你女朋友就一定分手<br />\n少少信任都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n番大陸有人同行有撚所謂咩<br />\n自己一個女仔返仲驚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你佔有欲咁強又做乜唔跟埋返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"894d8c4fe997f0260cd32d56785cda7e5826e304","t